Dear PharmEasy Support Team,

I am writing to follow up on the unresolved return request for Order ID
654541253527977984.

As previously informed, the Keraglo shampoo arrived with a loose cap,
causing leakage and spoiling the inner carton. I reported this on 7th
December 2025 with photographs and all required details. Since then, I have
repeatedly been assured that the item will be collected and the refund
processed.

However, the return pickup has failed again today. I even spoke with the
delivery person, who simply shrugged off his responsibility and stated that
he would not accept any damaged goods, despite the fact that he did not
even come to check the item.

This same situation has been ongoing since 8th December, where I keep
receiving messages that the return shipment will be picked up, yet no one
arrives.

This continued delay and lack of accountability is extremely unacceptable.

I request urgent intervention from your team to ensure that the pickup is
completed without further excuses and that the refund is processed promptly.

Kindly take immediate action and provide a resolution at the earliest.

Thank you.

Regards,
Sanjay Sharma

notes.body_html:
Hello Dushyant,

Greetings from PharmEasy!
​
With regards to your order #655484575831031808-63735, I see your order is at the confirmation stage and assigned for a Doctor Teleconsultation.

Our partner doctor tried contacting your multiple times. However, he was unable to connect with you. I am arranging a doctor callback on your registered mobile number 9828132323. You will be receiving a call within 2 hours. I would request you to answer the call so that the order could be processed further. I assure you the order will be processed on priority, once the Doctor consultation is completed. 

You can also reach out to us on 080-46161170 for your Doctor Consultation. 

Also, your order is estimated to be delivered to you within the timeline of 10th December 2025.

Your patience and understanding are highly appreciated in the meantime. 
​
For any further assistance, please reach out to us through our support channels in the App or website listed in the 'Need Help' section.

Thank you for choosing PharmEasy. Stay Healthy.

Regards,
Manisha

Dear Customer Support Team,
I had recently purchased my medicine from your platform and I am very
disappointed to tell you that there were two items missing in my package. I
literally paid for the missing items..like really? I had also tried to
contact your customer care number, but yet no response from your side and
at last I had to mail to you for your kind notice. This is not what I
expected from your end.

Two items that were missing are :-
1. NAZODROP AF 70 MD BOTTLE OF 9.8GM NASAL SPRAY
2. VOLINI PAIN RELIEF SPRAY 100GM

These two items are missing and yet I didn't got any resolution yet from
your side. I hope this mail finds you well and kindly provide me the
resolution for it. I want full refund for my missing order to my bank
account as it was COD. I had already updated my bank details on the app.
Kindly look into the matter and do the needful without further delay.

Please do the needful and let me know as soon as possible

Regards,
Aditya N
Mob No.- 8789527619

--

notes.body:
This is really the worst experience I have ever experienced in my life. I
had order total 3 items of which I had received only 1 item and rest 2 gone
missing. Perhaps as a customer I mailed and informed to your team the same
and now they are claiming that the medicines are being packed under CCTV
surveillance. Now what's the truth I don't know. If you guys sitting all
day for scaming people then that's the matter of fact I will not listen.
Because I had paid for the medicines, which I required through the
prescription uploaded and then also you guys cheated on the name of
medicines, knowing the emergency of the person...very good.
This really proves the dignity and mentality of such people working on
healthcare departments. It was hard earned money and I paid it for my need
and it's okk..Things will not be same..one or another day...it will gonna
pay back.

Indeed I will never again use your application in my life or will suggest
my friends or any family members again to use this platform for buying
medicines...I will do my job..I will get my medicines from another
platform. Don't worry..Keep it up.

It was my biggest mistake to trust on your platform for my medicines and
healthcare...Sorry guys but you lose a customer. I know it will not affect
your platform at all..but believe me...one day it will surely break the
chain.

I don't know who did this or whose fault it was..At last I will say...it
was a scam and I was cheated on this.

Be Grateful to yourselves..
Good Bye
